column5: Anyone flying out of Nakina with AWO? I have marked maps of most of their lakes and will forward to you. e-mail [email protected]
Flown with AWO many times. Actually helpd build the Melchett cabin expansion a few years back and the Kap Lake cabin as well.
Hasn't that area been closed to fishing for a few years. I wonder if anyone has any info on trappers run ? Thanks, Paul
